{"id":356105,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/71/337184.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"班固米做菜人","groupHref":"/group/zuocai","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/43/4324.jpg?r=1574965416","message":"&#x1F35C;&#x1F35C;&#x1F35C;&#x1F35C;&#x1F35C;<br>1. 准备红肠、生姜和半颗大料，大料去籽，红肠生姜切片改刀。<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_wCqYS.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_rng70.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_iXez0.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>2. 排骨剁块，用沸水焯水十分钟。<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_CCd2i.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>3. 锅内加少许油，再倒入焯过水的排骨，开中小火把排骨表面的水分煸干。加入大料生姜，接着煸炒 x 咱没留神，开大火炒的排骨和料头都烧焦了呜呜呜。<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_4wMf4.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_gXqGu.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>4. 加入两克盐、一汤匙料酒、两汤匙红烧汁和刚好没过排骨的清水，盖好锅盖焖煮 30 分钟！！！！！<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_7Lc7d.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_P717h.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_DDCab.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>5. 关火。将排骨和红肠码放在盛有大米的内胆中，淋上锅底的红烧汁，参照刻度线加适量清水。启动电饭煲，开始焖饭。<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_1AcQH.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_irq3D.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_A3sSj.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>6. 饭熟，取出内胆冷却，用盘子盖住电饭煲，将焖饭倒扣在盘子上面，再用另一个盘子倒扣，我的排骨红肠饭就可以出锅辣。<br><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_68wUB.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><img src=\"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/photo/l/ff/43/337184_xExLe.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/65.gif\" smileid=\"104\" alt=\"(bgm88)\"> 排骨我留了一半，，下次做焖饭一定做出美食博主内味儿 ~~~~ ","time":"2020-4-26 11:30","title":"排骨红肠饭","userId":"337184","userName":"haveatry","userSign":"(早安芥菜荠菜谷氨酸钠汤)"}